1 to the highest bidder after notice of such sale has been given by
2 publication at least three times for three consecutive weeks prior to the
3 date of sale in a legal newspaper of general circulation within the area
4 of the community improvement district.
5 (2) The articles of association shall state:
6 (a) The proposed community improvement district proposes an
7 aggregate maximum permitted levy rate for all purposes in an amount not
