1 the community improvement district.
2 (2) Except as otherwise provided, the board of trustees shall:
3 (a) Keep a record of all of its proceedings which shall be open to
4 inspection by all owners of real estate in the community improvement
5 district;
6 (b) Have the power to pass all necessary resolutions, orders, rules,
