3 being sought was elected solely by qualified resident voters or (b) at
4 least one qualified resident voter or qualified property owning voter if
5 the trustee whose recall is being sought was elected by qualified
6 resident voters and qualified property owning voters. Such voter or
7 voters shall be deemed to be the principal circulator or circulators of
