10 participated in the election of the trustee and shall request that the
11 filing clerk issue initial petition papers to the principal circulator
12 for circulation. The filing clerk shall notify the principal circulator
13 or circulators that the necessary signatures must be gathered within
14 thirty days after the date of issuing the petitions.
