19 one instrument, all petition papers comprising a recall petition for
20 signature verification with the filing clerk within thirty days after the
21 filing clerk issues the initial petition papers to the principal
22 circulator or circulators as provided in section 53 of this act.
23 (2) Within fifteen days after the filing of the petition, the filing
