4 years that the vacant lot has been platted within the corporate limits of
5 the city, whichever is applicable, (iv) the current assessed value of the
6 property within the redevelopment project area, (v) the increase in the
7 assessed value of the property within the redevelopment project area that
8 is estimated to occur as a result of the redevelopment project, (vi) an
9 indication of whether the redevelopment project will be financed in whole
10 or in part through the division of taxes as provided in section 18-2147,
11 and (vii) the agreed-upon costs of the redevelopment project;
