16 for the project; and
17 (c) The governing body shall determine whether to approve or deny
18 the redevelopment plan within thirty days after submission of the plan. A
19 redevelopment plan may be denied if:
20 (i) The redevelopment plan does not meet the requirements of
21 subsection (2) of this section;
22 (ii) Approval of the redevelopment plan would exceed the annual
