10 September 1, 2019, and August 31, 2020, as a result of a collective-
11 bargaining agreement in force and effect on September 1, 2017, that are
12 not otherwise included in an exclusion pursuant to subdivision (2)(d) of
13 this section, (vi) amounts levied in compliance with sections 79-10,110
14 and 79-10,110.02, and (vii) amounts levied to pay for special building
15 funds and sinking funds established for projects commenced prior to April
16 1, 1996, for construction, expansion, or alteration of school district
17 buildings. For purposes of this subsection, commenced means any action
18 taken by the school board on the record which commits the board to expend
19 district funds in planning, constructing, or carrying out the project.
