23 of Public Law 103-382, as such title existed on September 1, 2001. For
24 purposes of this subdivision, federal aid school district means any
25 school district which receives ten percent or more of the revenue for its
26 general fund budget from federal government sources pursuant to Title
27 VIII of Public Law 103-382, as such title existed on September 1, 2001.
